{"about_the_game":"<strong>The Swordfish: Knight of the Deep</strong> is a 2D underwater action-adventure. The game combines underwater traversal and out-of-water platforming.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Lore</h2>After an unprecedented storm, you find yourself trapped inside an underwater cave full of predators. While you anxiously try to find your way out, you discover a mysterious sword. As you pick it up, you feel its power flow through your veins, filling you with courage that sends you venturing deeper into the abyss. There you find a hidden world with wary creatures. They speak of an oppression that looms, which threaten their once blossoming kingdom.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a massive interconnected ocean world.<br></li><li>Face enemies and bosses that threaten the kingdom.<br></li><li>Acquire new weapons, items, and abilities as you progress.<br></li><li>Help friendly sea critters by completing tasks.<br></li><li>Overcome puzzling challenges along the way.<br></li><li>Fun mini-games and extras.<br></li><li>Cute pixel art and original soundtrack.<br></li><li>Compatible with most major console controllers.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784310/extras/the-swordfish.gif?t=1736358742\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736358742","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784310/page.bg.jpg?t=1736358742","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784310/5ae1ca2fcd17daf4d0af7c4611a094221bbf5391/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736358742","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1784310/5ae1ca2fcd17daf4d0af7c4611a094221bbf5391/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736358742","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id